   Retention Incentives for Early Care and Education Providers, Pilot
   Project

   1.)This is the application packet for County Commissions that will
   participate in the Retention Pilot Project during Fiscal Year 2001-02
   and Fiscal Year 2002-03.  All County Commissions that will participate
   must submit an application by September 5, 2001 (including those
   counties that submitted an application and participated in FY 2000-01).
   2.)Retention Incentives RFF Q & A, June 28, 2001
   3.)Retention Incentives RFF Q & A, July 27, 2001
   4.)Retention Incentives RFF Q & A, August 24, 2001 Revised


